{"tid":2232562,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"中國人是豬的傳人- 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-10-06T12:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-06T14:06:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c85d16af9d633a168f6c17b4f95772f6e9cdccc5","tid":2232562,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T12:51:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201006/UJ35KPSJWBAPJMG52J4HMRCRTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201006%2FUJ35KPSJWBAPJMG52J4HMRCRTE%2F&d=zpUJ%2F0Jv8gnTBnB6SvMaKCrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=03c4edd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201006%2FUJ35KPSJWBAPJMG52J4HMRCRTE%2F&h=935e0d29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201006/UJ35KPSJWBAPJMG52J4HMRCRTE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中國人是豬的傳人- 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Fd8DwSey6fThTUoKVHvirPFJBuA=/1920x1080/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FTFLAKLZZNGKLECDPZJC2NM6RE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFd8DwSey6fThTUoKVHvirPFJBuA%3D%2F1920x1080%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFTFLAKLZZNGKLECDPZJC2NM6RE.jpg&h=26279261&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月廿八日，中共中央政治局舉行第二十三次集體學習，由偉大舵手習近平主持。習近平提倡要努力建設有「中國特色、中國風格、中國氣派的考古學」，「繼續探索未知、揭示本源」，為弘揚中華優秀傳統文化、增強文化自信提供堅強支撐。連一個馬克思主義者也如此推崇中華文化，着實令人感動，但香港的所謂愛國藍絲KOL，居然無一響應。既然沒有人願意探索及揭示中華文化本源，我只好當仁不讓了。<br />\n<br />\n第一點必須揭示的就是：中華民族不是龍的傳人，而是豬的傳人。這不是我的觀點，而是湖南愛國學者黃守愚的研究結果。他旁徵博引，結合古文獻證據和現代考古發現，論證中華先民有豬靈崇拜的傳統。一般中國人只知道華夏最遠古的皇帝，是三皇五帝，但黃守愚則拈出莊子提過的豨韋氏。莊子稱豨韋氏「挈天地」（即開天闢地），古人注疏說「豨韋」是三皇以前帝號，比伏羲、神農、黃帝、堯、舜更遠古，而「豨」的意思，就是豬。<br />\n<br />\n黃守愚又說，「周易」的意思是「男男女女性交的豬靈廟」。。。。。。。。。。。。「都」為「豬」，故「周」本義就是豬，後來才引申為代表生殖的陽具。<br />\n<br />\n不但「周」是豬，周文王本身更是豬的「道成肉身」。今本《竹書紀年》有一節「中華版童貞產子」故事：「。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中國強大的主因，在「人多」，在繁殖方面，豬實在比龍更值得崇拜。請中國人不要忘本，從今以後，就正名為「豬的傳人」好了。"},{"pid":"fbad70650c7795e5c0297fe35b6975c27d9d5374","tid":2232562,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:26:05.000Z","msg":"圈養豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77363c13b14b0a2f2d24e2d881821ee9f0e27585","tid":2232562,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:27:31.000Z","msg":"遙遠的東方有一頭豬"},{"pid":"e8b2f9d47737466b3459c20a050299abe1779c7b","tid":2232562,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T13:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad05962203b28782e3ecba90de38357e8fdf5c2","tid":2232562,"uid":25073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T14:06:08.000Z","msg":"居然會用《竹書紀年》"}]}